---
import SectionHeading from './SectionHeading.astro';
---

<section class="what-is">
  <SectionHeading id="what-is">What is Markdown VDB?</SectionHeading>
  <p class="description">
    A filesystem-native vector database built around Markdown files.
    Powered by Rust, requiring zero infrastructure, and optimized for AI agents.
  </p>
  <div class="cards">
    <div class="card">
      <div class="icon">📁</div>
      <h3>Filesystem Native</h3>
      <p>Your Markdown files stay where they are. No importing, no syncing, no lock-in. The index lives alongside your content in a simple <code>.markdownvdb/</code> directory.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <div class="icon">⚡</div>
      <h3>Zero Infrastructure</h3>
      <p>No Docker, no databases, no servers. Install a single binary and start searching. Everything runs locally on your machine.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <div class="icon">🦀</div>
      <h3>Rust Performance</h3>
      <p>Sub-millisecond HNSW vector search, zero-copy deserialization, and memory-mapped indexes. Built for speed from the ground up.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .what-is {
    padding: 4rem 1.5rem;
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin-inline: auto;
  }

  .description {
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto 3rem;
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--color-text-muted, #8888aa);
  }

  .cards {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .card {
    background: var(--color-surface, #1a1a2e);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border, #2a2a4a);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg, 12px);
    padding: 2rem;
  }

  .icon {
    font-size: 2rem;
    color: var(--color-cyan, #00e5ff);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .card h3 {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', ui-monospace, monospace;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-text, #E0E0E0);
    margin: 0 0 0.75rem;
  }

  .card p {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--color-text-muted, #8888aa);
    margin: 0;
  }

  .card code {
    background: var(--color-bg, #0d0d1a);
    padding: 0.15em 0.4em;
    border-radius: 4px;
    font-size: 0.9em;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .cards {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
